      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（頂点を狙う、トップクラスのアイドルの一角だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They're part of the top-class idols aiming for the summit.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.333346063,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8400.003171000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "お、この間のライブバトルの記事出てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the article about the recent live battle is out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.36668879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『元BIG4のⅢX対実力派のやさぐれポメラニアン』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Former BIG4‚ ⅢX vs. The skilled‚ Rebellious Pomeranian\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6000221233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "『アイドルファンも唸る対戦カードだが、結果は』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"A matchup that even idol fans groan about‚ but the result is\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9000270904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふん……ふふん、私達のことべた褒めじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm hmm… hehe‚ they're praising us to the skies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.06668879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うわ。にやにや笑っちゃってさ、キモっ。kanaは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh. You're grinning like that‚ gross. kana is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9000251751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "まだ『元BIG4』呼ばわりされてんのに腹立つけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "still annoyed about being called \"former BIG4\" though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666968088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "貴方、ライブバトルで一回勝って、褒められただけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you satisfied just from winning one live battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7666918418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "満足してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and getting praised?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333634755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ。まさか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hah. no way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1000251751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "腑抜けてはいないようで何よりよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's good that you haven't gone soft.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3333585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "――私達の目的はただ一つ、トップに立つことだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Our goal is only one thing: reaching the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5333634755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まだまだ倒さないといけない奴らはいるんだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are still lots of guys we need to defeat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0666918418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "一度勝ったくらいで、浮かれてなんかいられないっつの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't get carried away just from winning once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8000301422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "残りのBIG4、それに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The remaining BIG4‚ and also…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "月スト、サニピ、トリエル、リズノワ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest‚ Sunny Peace‚ TRINITYAiLE‚ LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7666968088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "考えなければ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to think about",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8333585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "あの子達を倒すために、私達には何が必要なのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "what we need to defeat those girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333634755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それじゃ、また会議といきましょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ shall we have another meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8000251751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "観てる奴全員、驚かせてやろうじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's surprise everyone who's watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7000301422,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}